This home features 1.5 newly renovated bathrooms and a cozy family room, unique in this tranquil neighborhood. With spacious bedrooms, a large living room, and ample kitchen and dining space, it offers comfortable living. The patio and backyard are perfect for outdoor gatherings. Complete with a sizable 2-car garage and a storage shed, this property is ideal for those seeking a peaceful retreat or first-time home buyers.
